curam.omega3.util
Class FrequencySummary

java.lang.Object
  curam.omega3.util.FrequencySummary

public class FrequencySummary
extends java.lang.Object

This utility class displays a frequency pattern in its human language form. The nine character frequency pattern held on the server is parsed into readable language according to the entries in the associated properties file.
